snippet.title: Sega Saturn - Private Idol Disc Vol 05 - Fujisaki Nanako (1997)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Private Idol Disc Vol. 5: Fujisaki Nanako is a Miscellaneous game, developed and published by Sada Soft, which was released in Japan in 1997.
